1. "*Kažu* da se većina ljudi odlučuje za kupovinu automobila preko interneta." (They say that most people decide to buy a car over the internet.)

2. "Svi *kažu* da je to bilo veoma uspešno." (They all say that it was very successful.)

3. "Danas *kažu* da su vreme i novac dva najvrednija resursa." (They say today that time and money are two most valuable resources.)

4. "Neko *kaže* da se može postići uspeh bez mnogo truda." (Someone says that success can be achieved without much effort.)

5. "Mnogi *kažu* da je tehnologija napravila naš život lakšim." (Many say that technology has made our life easier.)